column5: Picked up my replica Bass my son and I caught last summer, sort of a team effort.  its a beauty! Great work by advanced taxidermy.
those guys do such a crazy good job. One of the best taxidermy/replica artists in the world without a doubt. How much did that big ol girl weigh? 8?
This one was around 6 pounds, bigger then any I've ever caught lol!
That,s awesome buddy . Look at that smile. Ear to ear . Good on ya dad.
Thanks! It looks great on the wall!, however it dwarfs the old bass I got mounted about 15 years ago lol!
The smile on the little guys face tells the whole story. Congrats to the pair of you.
Saweeeet fish and a great replica.
